title: The ORIGINAL "Sex Dwarf" music video from Soft Cell
description:
This is the long unavailable, banned, controversial, video of "Sex Dwarf" by "Tainted Love" songsters Soft Cell. When word leaked out about what this video contained the police were alerted and the original videos were seized and destroyed, except for a few that had already made it out of the facility. These were copied and circulated privately. Contains a dwarf, fetish gear, soft core sex, meat chainsaws, blood, lots of good stuff. I shared this video with a friend who remarked that he was simultaneously "proud and ashamed" that I&#039;d come upon something like this.

The quality isn&#039;t that good but it&#039;s not horrible.
